sentences: Kristian Paul Stanfill (born April 9, 1983) is an American Christian music singer, songwriter and worship leader from Atlanta, Georgia.
His album, Mountains Move (2011), reached No. 64 on the Billboard 200.
He is currently the worship pastor at Passion City Church and a worship leader at Passion Conferences.
